                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72112/1347a</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MIN1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morris</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 16, 1915</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. What is attitude Swedish Government toward cotton shipped from America to
                    Russia via Narvik, Norway, and through Sweden on through bills of lading?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
